### Cortex Hybrid Execution: Mix Standard & Cortex Processing
# Use Cortex for long parts, standard for short parts

POST https://cost-katana-backend.store/api/gateway/v1/chat/completions
CostKatana-Auth: Bearer YOUR_COSTKATANA_KEY
CostKatana-Enable-Cortex: true
CostKatana-Cortex-Hybrid-Execution: true
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "model": "gpt-4",
  "messages": [
    {"role": "user", "content": "Quick question: What is Kubernetes?"},
    {"role": "assistant", "content": "Kubernetes is..."},
    {"role": "user", "content": "Now write a comprehensive 2000-word guide on Kubernetes architecture, components, and best practices."}
  ]
}

